snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs Amber Heard LIVE Trial
snippet.description:
Link to my co-host claire
https://www.youtube.com/c/ClaireView307
Week 4 of the trial kicks off as were still hearing from JD's side. Expect Amber Heard to be on sometime this week.
Trial day 1 
https://youtu.be/IsT87oDIc6I
Trial day 2
https://youtu.be/FQZxYkteyQU

Trial day 3
https://youtu.be/nxciqxT81PE
Trial day 4
https://youtu.be/XVO7Jv2w1kA
Week 1 Recap
https://youtu.be/Ivv7Qt1CqeA

Week 2
Trial day 5
https://youtu.be/NPDAQY2fGSg
Trial day 6
https://youtu.be/EUtBchKJd_4
https://youtu.be/eUxzeK7PVLE --- Johnny Depp testifies
Trial day 7 
https://youtu.be/RCV-dNClAww --- Johnny Depp testifies against Amber Heard
Trial day 8 https://youtu.be/j5wVWMbh2W4 --- Johnny testifies and start of cross examination

Week 3
Trial day 9 https://youtu.be/MPPg2zdfn1s --- Johnny Depp still being cross exam ed along with new testimony from Ben King
Trial day 10 https://youtu.be/CtN7MRx4Shg
Trial day 11 https://youtu.be/_9dFuK463LM
Trial day 12 https://youtu.be/CxzbSYEQiNA
Day 9 recap https://youtu.be/hXdEvm-cll8
Day 10 recap https://youtu.be/Y1vsS5EEEPk
